                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6447" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0259</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8656 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合心机械：阿米巴经营的深化探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hexin Machinery：Deepening Exploration of Amoeba Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">霍明奎，张肃，李燕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长春理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长春合心机械制造有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿米巴经营；独立核算；人才培养；经营哲学；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Amoeba Management；Independent Accounting；Personnel Training； Management Philosophy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">摘要：本案例描述了长春合心机械制造有限公司（简称“合心机械”）在制造成本上升，企业利润水平快速下滑的困境下，通过引入阿米巴经营，实现组织模式创新，激发员工动力，从而提升效率、效能、效益，成为汽车零部件智能制造细分领域的世界隐形冠军。合心机械一直以来采用的是事业部制与项目制相结合的组织模式，在导入阿米巴经营的过程中，合心机械先后进行了多轮动员、宣传和集体学习活动，并成立第一事业部作为试点，之后又陆续成立七个阿米巴事业部，全面实行阿米巴经营。在实行阿米巴经营的几年时间内，合心机械确立了与市场直接挂钩的分部门核算制度；培养了大量具有经营者意识的人才；实现了以经营哲学为基础的全员参与的经营。合心机械通过全面覆盖阿米巴经营，人均产值、人均利润均有提升，员工离职率降低。未来，公司高层希望将合心机械阿米巴运营进一步深化。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes that Changchun Hexin Machinery Manufacturing Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Hexin machinery&quot;) has become the world invisible champion in the subdivided field of intelligent manufacturing of auto parts by introducing amoeba operation, realizing organizational model innovation and stimulating employee motivation, so as to improve efficiency, efficiency and benefit. Hexin machinery has always adopted the organization mode of combining business division system and project system. In the process of introducing amoeba management, Hexin machinery has carried out several rounds of mobilization, publicity and collective learning activities, and established the first business division as a pilot. After that, it has successively established seven amoeba business divisions to fully implement amoeba management. In the few years since the implementation of amoeba management, Hexin machinery has established a sub sector accounting system directly linked to the market; Trained a large number of talents with operator consciousness; It has realized the operation of full participation based on the management philosophy. Through the comprehensive coverage of amoeba business model, Hexin machinery has improved its per capita output value and per capita profit, and reduced the turnover rate of employees. In the future, the company&#39;s senior management hopes to further deepen the operation of Hexin machinery amoeba.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《组织管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革的原因;组织变革的征兆；组织变革的目标与根本目的；阿米巴经营的概念与内涵；组织变革的过程与程序；组织变革的阻力管理；组织变革的内容；阿米巴经营体系；组织变革的领导者；企业家精神
与组织文化；稻盛和夫：成功方程式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
